params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard visualizes traffic and threat patterns from AWS WAF logs integration.

This dashboard includes  request trends by action and rule, country and source distribution, top
IPs and blocked URL paths. Use this dashboard to monitor attacks, validate WAF rule performance, and detect unusual
traffic behavior.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/aws/overview?integration=waf)
